overview.en: AIOT Trusted Collaboration Environment (AT), which is based on DAG and graph database and supports edge architecture of highly available distributed accounts, is committed to building a credible Internet of Things collaboration and transaction execution environment.
overview.zh: AIOT Trusted (简称AT), 基于DAG和图数据库开发并支持边缘架构的高可用分布式账本，致力于构建一个可信的物联网协作以及交易执行环境。
